## [v1.0.0] – 2025-07-26

### 🎉 Initial Release

- 🚀 Project initialized for Summer of AI 2025
- ✍️ Story submission form created using Streamlit
- 💾 Stories stored directly into GitHub repo using GitHub token
- 🔊 Fun sound effect (success.mp3) plays after successful submission
- 🔥 Streak tracking feature implemented to boost engagement
- 🎨 Clean and mobile-friendly UI designed for rural audiences
- 🛡️ Licensed under GNU AGPLv3
- 📁 Organized file structure:
